{"tid":299033,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"係土耳其轉機既visa一問","createTime":"2017-06-26T17:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T10:24:33.000Z","uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b96f8bf93c9f89c9259b7e4dfa3586c6c55aab69","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"我黎緊去歐洲要係土耳其轉一程機<br />\n去個程就只係要等兩個半鐘<br />\n但係回程個程要係伊斯坦堡等成14個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果航空公司見到我有個咁長既layover, 又無Turkish visa<br />\n會唔會唔比我上機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係只要同航空公司講明我無打算入土耳其境, 淨係會留係離境區就得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係第一次有長過10個鐘既layover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbedb8aca98c7a31f16017012c39566b3e51ab68","tid":299033,"uid":122394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:34:21.000Z","msg":"唔知但幫推"},{"pid":"3bf07894de68e4b237c2e2300b2d53f0d2d017be","tid":299033,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎緊去歐洲要係土耳其轉一程機<br />\n去個程就只係要等兩個半鐘<br />\n但係回程個程要係伊斯坦堡等成14個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果航空公司見到我有個咁長既layover, 又無Turkish visa<br />\n會唔會唔比我上機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係只要同航空公司講明我無打算入土耳其境, 淨係會留係離境區就得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係第一次有長過10個鐘既layover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIf you hold a HKSAR passport, you can enter Turkey visa free for 90 days. Please see link below for details - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hongkong.cg.mfa.gov.tr/ShowInfoNotes.aspx?ID=160832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkong.cg.mfa.gov.tr%2FShowInfoNotes.aspx%3FID%3D160832&d=cBE4krt8N6%2Fd703qFEzApwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=07be9322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hongkong.cg.mfa.gov.tr/ShowInfoNotes.aspx?ID=160832</a>"},{"pid":"1b842042a10e0a42159b1d815734328545d394c0","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊去歐洲要係土耳其轉一程機<br />\n去個程就只係要等兩個半鐘<br />\n但係回程個程要係伊斯坦堡等成14個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果航空公司見到我有個咁長既layover, 又無Turkish visa<br />\n會唔會唔比我上機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係只要同航空公司講明我無打算入土耳其境, 淨係會留係離境區就得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係第一次有長過10個鐘既layover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIf you hold a HKSAR passport, you can enter Turkey visa free for 90 days. Please see link below for details - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hongkong.cg.mfa.gov.tr/ShowInfoNotes.aspx?ID=160832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkong.cg.mfa.gov.tr%2FShowInfoNotes.aspx%3FID%3D160832&d=cBE4krt8N6%2Fd703qFEzApwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=07be9322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hongkong.cg.mfa.gov.tr/ShowInfoNotes.aspx?ID=160832</a></blockquote><br />\n我知SAR Passport有visa free啊<br />\n不過我無SAR passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 唔該哂巴打既資訊"},{"pid":"4069bab02ce498148d5239f744bd8f97986eb5c5","tid":299033,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎緊去歐洲要係土耳其轉一程機<br />\n去個程就只係要等兩個半鐘<br />\n但係回程個程要係伊斯坦堡等成14個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果航空公司見到我有個咁長既layover, 又無Turkish visa<br />\n會唔會唔比我上機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係只要同航空公司講明我無打算入土耳其境, 淨係會留係離境區就得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係第一次有長過10個鐘既layover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無問題，大把人係機場打地鋪。  我都試過坐8個鐘，好難頂。"},{"pid":"a2a79a52163b1d69a698237bd4dae53d6de59db4","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104ed29b649c97178b6449bbe95c89cc64a3bf6b","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5864f8ab1d34b4161b60b14f5dc626de1a5f9e3b","tid":299033,"uid":46838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:41:23.000Z","msg":"試過等12個鐘轉機去烏克蘭<br />\n<br />\n係香港上機前我問返地勤我係等緊途中可唔可以出去行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122fb7624576be817905bd96ac6f3ea5c17551f2","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊去歐洲要係土耳其轉一程機<br />\n去個程就只係要等兩個半鐘<br />\n但係回程個程要係伊斯坦堡等成14個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果航空公司見到我有個咁長既layover, 又無Turkish visa<br />\n會唔會唔比我上機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係只要同航空公司講明我無打算入土耳其境, 淨係會留係離境區就得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係第一次有長過10個鐘既layover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無問題，大把人係機場打地鋪。  我都試過坐8個鐘，好難頂。</blockquote><br />\n我試過打過六個鐘地鋪<br />\n最仆街係有時d關員會隔一兩個鐘就走過黎拍你起身叫你show passport<br />\n<br />\n但係十幾個鐘layovers我就真係未試過"},{"pid":"b8099a8718e6d06b363d10eeffd146b7c29758ec","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過等12個鐘轉機去烏克蘭<br />\n<br />\n係香港上機前我問返地勤我係等緊途中可唔可以出去行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當時巴打你係土耳其轉機係用特區定係BNO/BC/其他passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無乜打算出去行下, 但係我有d驚連機都上唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以家下諗緊好唔好上網整定個e-visa先"},{"pid":"7d947c820a68858baeaa789baa941827a397d586","tid":299033,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎緊去歐洲要係土耳其轉一程機<br />\n去個程就只係要等兩個半鐘<br />\n但係回程個程要係伊斯坦堡等成14個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果航空公司見到我有個咁長既layover, 又無Turkish visa<br />\n會唔會唔比我上機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係只要同航空公司講明我無打算入土耳其境, 淨係會留係離境區就得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係第一次有長過10個鐘既layover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會唔俾你上機, 只要你唔入境就OK<br />\n不過好似有得上網整VISA, 你咪整左先, 到時睇下入唔入境"},{"pid":"80f0ad5f7308faf772720cd577b97947e732844c","tid":299033,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"同埋你搭咩航空公司, 佢有轉機counter就唔需要入境<br />\n無既話你要入左境再出境咁轉機, 你唔清楚既話其實可以問你航空公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f570f27ce827e100556d6c45cc9f5f64a70936f1","tid":299033,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋你搭咩航空公司, 佢有轉機counter就唔需要入境<br />\n無既話你要入左境再出境咁轉機, 你唔清楚既話其實可以問你航空公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nanyway唔該哂巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搭Turkish Airlines啊, 係Istanbul Atat&uuml;rk 内轉機<br />\n我諗應該有轉機counter掛, 因為Turkish Airlines個main base就係Atat&uuml;rk Airport<br />\n但係我會再上網睇清楚<br />\n<br />\n其實我都諗緊好唔好整定個e-visa, 反正好似好平, 整定無壞<br />\n不過我係想上黎問下之前有無人係試過類似情況咁解<br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9e4a6b013527c37df8d673eebd15d25e8108aa","tid":299033,"uid":122151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋你搭咩航空公司, 佢有轉機counter就唔需要入境<br />\n無既話你要入左境再出境咁轉機, 你唔清楚既話其實可以問你航空公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nanyway唔該哂巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搭Turkish Airlines啊, 係Istanbul Atat&uuml;rk 内轉機<br />\n我諗應該有轉機counter掛, 因為Turkish Airlines個main base就係Atat&uuml;rk Airport<br />\n但係我會再上網睇清楚<br />\n<br />\n其實我都諗緊好唔好整定個e-visa, 反正好似好平, 整定無壞<br />\n不過我係想上黎問下之前有無人係試過類似情況咁解<br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次搭TK係Istanbul轉機唔需要入境<br />\n仲有上次去果陣layover time 多過5小時既話，<br />\n可以去無記錯係Gate 216附近個TK counter果度拎一餐免費飯<br />\n你自己去研究下仲有冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c76ad738004ad00d4bc333b329212b7f88b605","tid":299033,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"唔係所有人都有TWOV,<br />\n<br />\n你係咩國籍先"}]}